values:
I spent the night with Anthony last night,whenever we do that it makes me feel so much closer to him and then when the next night comes I feel miserable.  He was kinda a dick head yesterday to me throughout the day, he was talking with his guys about how he fucked the rat face lookin girl that works at the gas station, and I got pissed off. He said that I try to act like I am his girl and shit, what a prick, cuz honestly, we do things that couples do, and Im sorry Im not a fucken hoe and I actually sleep with the poeple I care about...I dont know, I love him to death and I pray like every night that we will be together, and I  hope someday he will realize that I can make him happy if he gives me the chance....

Laura, Jina, Sam S. and Sam M. all hung out today after I worked.  We just drove around and went to Taco Bell, the usual shit, then we went over to Alex's house, we just sat around, they were having a little pre-memorial day bash and mandy's bday party.  It was so ackward being there, seeing as my former best friend use to live there, now she is in New York, I guess she is coming to town next weekened and staying for 3 weeks, I will try and call her, I wanted to get the "BSG" back together, but it probably will not work out...

Well, I am getting tired, and as usual I gotta work tommorw, so im gonna hit the hay....peace out!!

Well, my day really wasnt that great, I worked until 9 am, today was Mike's last day, thank god, I only like to work when Sandy is there. Anyway, I got home, went to sleep, then Anthony called, he is being a sweetheart these last few days, then, hung out with laura, her mom, and her sister, we went to shakeys, and what luck, we got some really cool prizes from in the game room. haha, anyway, then we went by jina's and then by somalia's (sam s.) house!
I just wrote all kinds of stuff in here, and it somehow didnt even work...well, next time, at least I got shit off my chest...even though it wont show on here!
